<p>When you register with Onestoryroad, you create your own profile. Your profile information, as well as your name, email and photo, are displayed to people in the story page to enable you to connect with people on Onestoryroad. We may occasionally use your name and email address to send you notifications regarding new services offered by Onestoryroad that we think you may find valuable.</p>
</br>
