</br>
<p>Generally, you may opt out of such emails by a personal email to onestoryroad.com, though Onestoryroad reserves the right to send you notices about your account even if you opt out of all voluntary email notifications.</p>
</br>
<p>Onestoryroad may use information in your profile without identifying you as an individual to third parties. We do this for purposes such as aggregating how many people in a network like a story and personalizing advertisements and promotions so that we can provide you Onestoryroad. We believe this benefits you. You can know more about the world around you and, where there are advertisements, they're more likely to be interesting to you. </p>
</br>
<p>We may use information about you that we collect from other sources, including but not limited to newspapers and Internet sources such as blogs, instant messaging services, and other users of Onestoryroad, to supplement your profile. Where such information is used, we generally allow you to specify in your privacy settings that you do not want this to be done or to take other actions that limit the connection of this information to your profile (e.g., removing photo tag links).</p>
